22 WHEREAS, President Donald J. Trump has nominated former Governor of
23 Arkansas Michael Dale "Mike" Huckabee as United States Ambassador to Israel
24 in recognition of former Governor Huckabee's extensive experience, passion,
25 and commitment to the United States-Israel alliance; and
26
27 WHEREAS, former Governor Huckabee was a three-term Governor of
28 Arkansas, is a Baptist minister, and is well-known as an advocate for Israel,
29 and therefore he brings a unique combination of political expertise, faith-
30 driven values, and personal ties to the Israeli region; and
31
32 WHEREAS, former Governor Huckabee has been a vocal supporter of
33 Israel's right to sovereignty and self-defense, rooted in his personal
34 beliefs and unwavering support for democracy in the Israeli region; and
35
36 WHEREAS, former Governor Huckabee's nomination highlights the universal
